</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_332_r2l1">Werd </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ladung <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l3">Matheis Cʒeſel des Frıcʒen Cʒeſels
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Sun / <del rend="strikethrough"> als
                                    <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan></del> ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l4">vnd die <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / . <expan>Laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l5">derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd ſein Sun der cʒeit nicht anheim
                        ſind </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l6">vnd wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> Cʒeſels wirtin / darvmb beſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l7">vnd die ſprichet / daʒ Jr darvmb nicht empfolhen ſeÿ
                        / . Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l8"><expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ew kein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſie <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l9">
<add><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l1">daʒ vvir Jr </ab><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l2">rede auch </ab><ab facs="#facs_332_r1l3"><expan>hört<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab></add>
<expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> reden laſſen mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>klagfür<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l10"><expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> doch vnſer
                                <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht ıſt / daʒ
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeinen <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        darcʒü <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l11">wil / daʒ man die klag ſchieb bıs auf das nehſt
                        Gerıchte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l13">nach ſant <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Galle<ex>n</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_332_line_1576488006233_5148">Mıchels </ab></add> tag
                        ſchirſt / . vnd wenn ſie <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> her heim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l14"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt es dann daʒ
                                <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> daran mant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l15">So wöllen wir Jr rede auch hören / vnd ew
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l16"><expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vvıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> laſſen / vnd wo vvir ew lıeb vnd
                                <expan>früntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l17"><expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir
                        allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_332_r2l18"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Egıdij / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_332" id="165v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Werd </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ladung <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        als Matheis Czesel, des Friczen Czesels, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, sun, ew und die
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wissen, daz derselb
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> und sein sun der czeit nicht anheim
                        sind. Und wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> Czesels wirtin darumb besant und die
                        sprichet, daz ir darumb nicht empfolhen sey. Nu
                            <expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew kein
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, sie <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim, <add>daz wir ir rede auch
                                    <expan>hört<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>.
                            <expan>Dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> reden lassen mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>klagfür<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> doch unser
                                <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht ist, daz
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> seinen <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        darczü <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wil, daz man die klag schieb bis auf
                        das nehst gerichte <app><note><q type="date">nach sant <add>Michels</add> tag schirst</q>29.09.1411</note></app>. Und wenn sie
                                <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan> her heim
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>, ist es dann, daz
                            <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> daran mant, so wöllen wir ir rede auch hören
                        und ew <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen. Und wo wir ew lieb und
                                <expan>früntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
